    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <span>Scroll</span>
    <div class="scroll-dot"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="section-label">About Us</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Nurturing Minds,<br><span>Shaping Futures</span></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Manglam Vidhyalaya is a premier educational institution located in the heart of Halvad, Gujarat. With a steadfast commitment to academic excellence and holistic development, we prepare every student to face tomorrow's challenges with confidence.</p>
        <p>Our dedicated faculty, modern facilities, and value-based curriculum create an environment where curiosity thrives, character is built, and every child discovers their true potential.</p>
        <p>We believe education is not just about textbooks — it is about inspiring a love for learning, fostering creativity, and building responsible citizens of tomorrow.</p>
        <div class="values-row">
          <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon">📚</div><h4>Excellence</h4><p>High academic standards in every classroom</p></div>
          <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon">🌱</div><h4>Growth</h4><p>Holistic development of mind, body & spirit</p></div>
          <div class="value-card"><div class="value-icon">🤝</div><h4>Values</h4><p>Integrity, respect and community service</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-logo">
        <img src="/mnt/user-data/uploads/1000041266.jpg" alt="School Logo" class="about-logo-img"/>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-dark);font-size:1.05rem;">"The Vision for Future"</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.4rem;color:#6A7A8A;font-size:0.82rem;">Opp. Meldidham, Sara Road, Halvad</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<section id="stats">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-item"><h3>500+</h3><p>Students Enrolled</p></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><h3>30+</h3><p>Expert Faculty</p></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><h3>100%</h3><p>Pass Rate</p></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><h3>10+</h3><p>Years of Excellence</p></div>
